{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<msqrt>","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","hasMathML":true,"sidebarHTML":"\n    <ol>\n        <li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element\">MathML Reference</a></strong>\n\n        \n            </li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\">&lt;math&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\">&lt;menclose&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/merror\">&lt;merror&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\">&lt;mpadded&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom\">&lt;mphantom&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot\">&lt;mroot&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow\">&lt;mrow&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\">&lt;ms&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt\">&lt;msqrt&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\">&lt;mstyle&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\">&lt;munderover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/semantics\">&lt;semantics&gt;</a></li>\n        \n\n        \n    </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>MathMLの <code>&lt;msqrt&gt;</code> 要素は平方根（根指数のついていない累乗根）を表示するために用いられます。 引数は一つだけで、構文は <code>&lt;msqrt&gt; <em>base</em> &lt;/msqrt&gt;</code> となります。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"attr-class-id-style\">class, id, style</dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a>を用いて修飾を行なう際に使われます。</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-href\">href</dt>\n <dd>ハイパーリンクを設定する際に用いられます。</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-mathbackground\">mathbackground</dt>\n <dd>数式の背景色を指定するために使われます。<code>#rgb</code><font face=\"Arial, x-locale-body, sans-serif\">、</font><code>#rrggbb</code>のような16進表現のほか、HTMLで定められた<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#color_keywords\" rel=\"noopener\">色キーワード</a>を用いることができます。</dd>\n <dt id=\"attr-mathcolor\">mathcolor</dt>\n <dd>根号を含んだ数式の文字の色を指定するために使われます。<code>#rgb</code><font face=\"Arial, x-locale-body, sans-serif\">、</font><code>#rrggbb</code>のような16進表現のほか、HTMLで定められた<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#color_keywords\" rel=\"noopener\">色キーワード</a>を用いることができます。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>レンダリングのサンプル(画像): <img alt=\"root-x\" src=\"/files/3201/msqrt.png\" style=\"margin-left: 10px; vertical-align: middle;\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n\n<p>ブラウザのレンダリング結果: <math> <msqrt> <mi>x</mi> </msqrt> </math></p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>msqrt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>x<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>mi</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>msqrt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザごとの互換性","id":"ブラウザごとの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"mathml.elements.msqrt","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML3/chapter3.html#presm.msqrt\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 3.0<br><small lang=\"ja\">msqrt の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td>Current specification</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML2/chapter3.html#presm.msqrt\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 2.0<br><small lang=\"ja\">msqrt の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td>Initial specification</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot\" title=\"<mroot>\">&lt;mroot&gt;</a></code> (Radical with an index)</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"ブラウザごとの互換性","id":"ブラウザごとの互換性"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"MathMLの <msqrt> 要素は平方根（根指数のついていない累乗根）を表示するために用いられます。 引数は一つだけで、構文は <msqrt> base </msqrt> となります。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<msqrt>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<msqrt>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<msqrt>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/mathml/element/msqrt","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/mathml/element/msqrt/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けの